      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like it's just a \"phase\" or lost purpose. it feels like it's actually finished. like the story ended years ago and i'm just reading the same blank pages over and over. there's no point in trying to \"find\" someone who isn't there anymore. it's just exhausting to keep pretending the person inside still exists.",
