      "content": "it's just so much work... to keep this shell moving. the \"characters\" you're talking about, they're just echoes. it feels like there's no dignity in just lingering when everything that made life worth living is already gone. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just... let the story truly close? instead of this endless, repetitive nothingness?",
